---
title: BBQ Beef and Mozzarella Flatbread Pizzas with Apple and Mixed Greens Salad
description: Rumor has it that BBQ sauce makes everything better. Paired with succulent ground beef and ooey gooey mozzarella, sweet and tangy BBQ sauce creates a truly memorable pizza dinner.
